headline: Garmin (NYSE:GRMN) Launches Garmin Connect+ For Enhanced Health Insights With AI Features
summary: Garmin (NYSE:GRMN) recently witnessed a 4% price increase over the past week, coinciding with its announcement of Garmin Connect+, a premium plan enhancing the user experience of its smartphone app. This positive momentum may also be linked to its G3000® PRIME selection by Pilatus for military training aircraft and integration with Clippd to boost golf performance analytics, showcasing unique AI-driven features.
